# Backlog MVP (v0.1)

1. Auth API (register/login/logout) via Sanctum
2. Create Transfer: POST /api/transfers (CREATED)
3. List Transfers: GET /api/transfers (pagination)
4. Show Transfer: GET /api/transfers/{id}
5. Rate/Fee: calcul simple (config statique)
6. Status transitions contrôlées (machine)
7. Payment placeholder: endpoint "mark paid" (admin/operator)
8. Provider stub: simulate payout + retry
9. Audit log: track actions (status change, notes)
10. Roles/Seed: admin/operator/user
